modName: Tree LOD for Skysight Simply Bigger Trees
summary: Scaled up Trees LOD for SSBT mod to lessen pop ins
descriptionHtml:
My personal trees LOD for an awesome [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/56877/]SSBT[/url] plugin by fadingsignal.
Decided to upload it because SSBT doesn't have a proper LOD yet.
Generated for vanilla Skyrim game using SSBT only, don't try to mix with other tree changing mods like SFO.
Also added dead reach trees LOD as a bonus which is missing in vanilla game.
author: zilav
